"msg":"好似一戴一露咁問鄰國借錢，還唔到就割地還 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e976367b1b428eb93020e2e34b094e79695d49","tid":2300912,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"要欖炒有咩所謂、 政府d錢唔用係明日大嶼，連登仔唔係以為有得分掛、快d動工喇"},{"pid":"865f83f17270026802e265c731407b91eb6a5614","tid":2300912,"uid":83782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:47:46.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦 佢玩死香港最多咪移民"},{"pid":"457028180a4c426f279d532c67e1f9f29f5836f0","tid":2300912,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"GOOD JOB  玩到負資產就最好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c6411421a809b48cfc202ae389aa129ddaf38f","tid":2300912,"uid":105219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:39:17.000Z","msg":"只要拎市民的強積金去填海就夠數"}]}